{"tid":1252650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭伊健大讚達哥：投資遊戲好有誠意，非常欣賞達哥，值得支持。","createTime":"2019-06-23T06:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T17:29:34.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad77137b2d105c985b8a654d2658e9ceb0fd534","tid":1252650,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181107/_2018110717085033305.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181107%2F_2018110717085033305.jpg&h=09c9b5f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭伊健出席電競手機活動，正忙於籌備演唱會的他會否沒時間打機？他說不會，好多資訊可參考手機遊戲，以前有新構思只可用口來表達，現時可透過手機遊戲。他指出上次演唱會有人覺得好前衛，其實好多意念也來自遊戲機，甚至好多新電影世界也來自遊戲機，包括配樂，遊戲機發展比電影要快，所以他會繼續打機。至於演唱會會否參考手機遊戲？他笑言剛才的遊戲也是抄他們，大家互相啟發，從中發掘新元素。<br />\n<br />\n伊健開心建立這個形像，以前拍戲經常被人說他這個年紀還掛住打機，他反問現時全世界誰不打機？證明自己行得比大家快，打機成為自己的興趣，好彩不是買跑車，打機平很多。不過近年他以環保角度少換科技，強調不是不玩，只是看準一點去玩。<br />\n<br />\n現場與新一代機神「達哥」打機，伊健指對方投資遊戲好有誠意，他也想做，但要有自己的班底，若有機會也希望投放及參與，甚麼遊戲便要考慮清楚，他開心見到有廣東話遊戲，認為值得支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181107/_2018110717085120561.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181107%2F_2018110717085120561.jpg&h=2c564128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1359027/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1359027%2F&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=67db685a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1359027%2F&h=f6dc9662\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1359027/</a>"},{"pid":"1ab8dcade9ea0d5fef73378d274e584260f56e9d","tid":1252650,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348f36c58e5c3aa360c371df6c67d3ee4a3f1c35","tid":1252650,"uid":55552,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:31:43.000Z","msg":"含撚啦死迖狗"},{"pid":"839a4bb53abc9e85dcb455084fe1de2ec3bf8ad5","tid":1252650,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}